The paper deals with image translation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a deep attention encoder and generative adversarial networks (GANs), which are popular techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the discovery of instance-level correspondences, which is related to geometric reasoning (cs.GR) and multimodal learning (cs.MM).
